➜“空巢”不“空心”
http://www.sohu.com/a/429864256_114731	4941
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201106/599a20cbcd194a33b47111d25000e3bc.jpeg" width="509" height="348" /></p>
